## 📂 Key Files

```
kgd-app/
├── src/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── (app)/        # All protected pages
│   │   │   ├── dashboard/
│   │   │   ├── customers/
│   │   │   ├── invoices/
│   │   │   ├── payments/
│   │   │   ├── products/
│   │   │   ├── inventory/
│   │   │   └── audit/
│   │   └── login/
│   ├── actions/          # Server actions (DB mutations)
│   ├── components/       # InvoiceForm client component
│   └── lib/              # prisma, auth, utils, audit
├── prisma/
│   ├── schema.prisma     # 11 models
│   └── seed.ts           # Initial data
└── prisma.config.ts      # Prisma 7 config (DB URL here)
```

---

## 💡 Key Business Rules Implemented

- **Variable rates**: Invoice line items always require manual rate confirmation (pre-filled from product default but fully editable)
- **Partial payments**: Payment allocation shows each open invoice with balance due
- **Customer ledger**: `/customers/[id]` shows combined invoice + payment timeline with running balances
- **Soft deletes**: Customers and products use `isActive` flag, never hard-deleted
- **Admin-only actions**: Cancel invoice, delete contact, deactivate customer, view audit log
- **Audit trail**: Every create/update is logged with old/new values and the user who made the change

